attributes.title: PROFESSOR OAK'S FUNERAL • POKEMON LET'S GO
attributes.description: Welcome to Pokemon Let's Goooooo! A new series on Cow Chop where Aleks and James start their Pokemon collecting adventure. But there's a twist! They can only catch and keep one Pokemon per zone. If they catch another Pokemon in that zone, they have to be sent to Professor Oak  and crushed into candy. Perma-death is ON. If a pokemon faints in battle, they will be sent to Professor Oak and crushed into candy. It's very morbid.

attributes.title: HARD AS A ROCK • POKEMON LET'S GO EP. 2
attributes.description: Pokemon Let's GOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO is back with more one sided fights against Weedles.  But more importantly, what is this game like with James holding the ball?  Only one way to find out, dive deep and lets GOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!

attributes.title: POKEMON IMPERSONATIONS • POKEMON LET'S GO EP. 3
attributes.description: We're back with the 3rd installment of Pokemon Let's Go Pikachu Cowhop Nuzlocke Perma Death Challenge Edition!!  God damn that's a title!! Aleks is back to fondling those Pokeballs and shoving them in the face of every Pokemon challenger he sees.  Guess nothings new.

attributes.title: POKEMON ON THE STREETS • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: Sitting on the couch playing video games is for weaklings!!!  Luckily we happen to be the strongest men on the planet, so naturally we run around playing only the greatest games like Pokemon GO!!!  Wanna be super fit like us?  Well too bad!!!  Sit down and watch this video instead!!!

attributes.title: GOTTA CRINGE EM ALL • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: The cringe is strong in this episode of Pokemon GO!!!  At least for Aleks.  Want to watch a grown man dress like a child and then immediately regret it?  Then this is the perfect episode for your enjoyment!!!

attributes.title: DEATH IS CALLING • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: After the embarrassment of being in public catching Pokemon and questioning the very nature of reality, the boys hide (I mean head) back inside to comfort of the couch.  The only problem?  They're not alone.  It seems misery loves company.

attributes.title: NOBS 4... LYF? • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: Who loves filler episodes?  Who knows maybe something will happen in this episode to make it worth while.  Maybe some crazy M. Night Shyamalan twist or something.  Only one way to find out!!

attributes.title: THE SEXIEST POKEMON TRAINER • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: When we last left our duo they were in the middle of a heated battle just like they every 5 minutes.  Luckily you are in store for a lot more fun!!!  At least I think you are.  I'm not really sure.  I probably should've watched this episode before writing this.  Oh well, best of luck boys!!!

attributes.title: WHO'S THAT PATREON • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: Not all the cringe in the world could keep Aleks and James off the street in search of more Pokemon.  Luckily though, they happen to know a few trainers who decided to get involved with the hunt.  Not a single person decided that this was a good idea!!!  Many thanks to our Patreons!  We love you!

attributes.title: BIOHAZARD DESTRUCTION • Rainbow Six Siege Gameplay
attributes.description: Teamwork and cooperation are encouraged in Siege, and players need to take advantage of their different abilities in order to complete the objective and defeat the enemy team.  There are different types of modes; the guys are playing the "secure area" mode in which the defenders must protect a room with biohazard containers, while the attackers must fight their way in. The match ends when all players from one team are killed or the biohazard container is secured by the attackers when there are no defenders in the room.

attributes.title: SURVIVAL OF THE GAMER • Rainbow Six Siege Gameplay

attributes.title: AN AWKWARD LOVE STORY • Rainbow Six Siege Gameplay
attributes.description:
While Jakob's off at war with the ghouls, his wife is withering away. Will he make it back to her before it's too late or will Asher and Aleks become his new love interest. Or are they too interested in each other? 

After a space capsule crashed in New Mexico, an Outbreak and a surge of violence forced the authorities to establish a Quarantine Zone around Truth or Consequences. Outbreak challenges you to step up to the plate. Go on the offensive and venture inside the Quarantine Zone to contain the infection threatening to spread across North America. Explore our three new maps with your squad and survive hordes of hostiles to identity the source of the parasite.

attributes.description: Dragon Ball FighterZ is a 2.5D fighting game based on the Dragon Ball franchise. Players each select three characters to form a team. One character is controlled, and can be switched with one of their other characters at any time. Players can also call one of their other characters to perform an "Assist" move, allowing simultaneous attacks and combos with the entire team. All three of the opponent's characters must be defeated to win the game. Today the first four of six Cow Chop competitors go head to head in the first half of our first annual Official Cow Chop SoCal Tournament 2018, which we don't plan on having next year; so this is it really.

DESOLATE is a first person horror survival experience. Join Aleks, James, Trevor and Jakob as they team up and explore an open world filled with mysteries and unsolved questions. 

In this episode, the gang runs into controversy as they discover Aleks has died and left a baby out in the cold. Social services (Jakob) has to come to take the baby away, deeming Aleks unfit to care for the young child. Only Trevor has the opportunity next to adopt this abandoned baby and become the father figure he never had. But can Trevor ever quit doing rails of adderall and sniffing spores? If not, the only option left to take care of this poor baby is James, but....... is he even playing the same game?

attributes.description: Secret Hitler is a social deduction game for 5-10 people about finding and stopping the Secret Hitler. Players are secretly divided into two teams: the liberals, who have a majority, and the fascists, who are hidden to everyone but each other. If the liberals can learn to trust each other, they have enough votes to control the elections and save the day. But the fascists will say whatever it takes to get elected, advance their agenda, and win the game.

attributes.title: HOW WE FIXED THIS BROKEN ALIENS GAME
attributes.description: Back in 2013 a game called "Alien Colonial Marines" came out and it went straight from a dream to a disaster. Five years later, a devoted fan went into the game code to try to create a playable version. Turns out it came down to just one letter. Today Aleks and James are playing side by side and comparing the two versions: The launch version and the repaired code version. Does it make a difference? Or does the game still suck?

attributes.title: CRAZY MUTE CHARADES
attributes.description:
What is Crazy Mute? It’s a King of Charades ;)
All you have to do is explain the word you see on your card to other players using only your body language, gestures and facial expressions.

attributes.title: DEATH METAL SNOWPIT
attributes.description:
THE 19TH CENTURY
It was supposed to be the peak of human achievement.
Instead, it turned out to be the end of our civilization.
Now, as the ruler of the last city on Earth, it is your duty to manage both its citizens and the infrastructure. What decisions will you make to ensure society’s survival? What will you do when pushed to the breaking point?
Who will you become in the process?
Do what it takes as…
THE CITY MUST SURVIVE

OR JUST THROW THE BODIES INTO THE SNOW PIT
